            "name": "operations",
            "description": " - INVALID: place-holder for impossible situations\n - READ: ead from a dataset\n - WRITE: rite to a dataset, create children of a directory\n - VIEW: s an entity visible (could be a dataset, role, user, directory...)\n - ADMIN: an permissions on an entity be modified?\n - USEROLE: an a role be used in an ACL?\n - APPLYROLE: an a role be added to a principal?\n - VOUCHFOR: can a plugin vouch for an identity?",
